The dataset studied¶

Dogs ratings tweets from the famous twitter account WeRateDogs.

Analysis¶

In this analysis I tried to find correlations between people's favorite dogs and their corresponding number of retweets, I was also able to life stages in dogs and their degree of popularity.

1- Life stages : I found that among those who gave information about their dogs stages the most frequent ones were puppers as it is shown in the bar graph below :

It's a bit tricky to come to conclusion that pupper are the most common or popular life stage in dogs as the dataset has lots of null values

According to the scatter plot above, it is clear there is a strong association beween people's favorite dogs and their corresponding number of retweets.
